    <briefdescription>
<para>Bluetooth data. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Description of different AD Types that can be encoded into advertising data. Used to form arrays that are passed to the <ref refid="group__bt__gap_1gad2e3caef88d52d720e8e4d21df767b02" kindref="member">bt_le_adv_start</ref> function. The <ref refid="group__bt__gap_1ga8481217e632522e1f322de87d745f8f0" kindref="member">BT_DATA</ref> define can be used as a helpter to declare the elements of an <ref refid="structbt__data" kindref="compound">bt_data</ref> array. </para>
